Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. But, since I still have to introduce my patients to other hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'm having the hospital in Aomori wait for me till I'm done with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And besides,\NI have to go to court to testify on the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,case the happened here, to support Mr. Mouri's deduction.
