Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only ones who are staying in this apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,without running away are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bancho and Mr. Yotsuya that you just saw a while ago and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,me, living in Room No.5 on the second floor, just the three of us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So half of the eight residents moved out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because of the ghost scare...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It began when I saw a death candle floating
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in that building next door at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, none of the residents in this apartment believed me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But suddenly after the water of the toilet turned bloody red,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and, a pale figure of a person was seen through the window
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the residents suddenly began feeling faint and seeing dreadful hallucinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange and eetsie things happened one after the other
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, media people-TV reporters and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,magazines journalists used come and interview us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why didn't you move out, gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,} I'm old and have not much time to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there is nothing for me to be scared of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also I don't want to move out of my dear old house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you're welcome to stay as long as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the ghost doesn't want to come out till
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're leaving now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
