Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it sounds very interesting too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, ¢'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, ¢'mon!
