Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you had a nightmare or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No! I really saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops, its this late already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gee, how could I have fallen asleep like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go to the john.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wake that gramps up and tell him that we're heading on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ghosts, my foot! Talk about ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was nothing but a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This toilet is so stinkand, dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is full of dead insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heck
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should've left here earlier just as Ran said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:05.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't wake the old man up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a minute. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-W-What's up, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The toilet water is blood red!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's all the commotion about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toilet water is blood red, my father said
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! I knew she'd come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is someone's idea of a sick joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,put red paint in the tank water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:51.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I.guess not
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you had blood in your urine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No darn way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh WI flushed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The water turned the color of blood all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A dreadful illusion appearing after feeling faint
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Water suddenly turning red.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, all that's left to happen is
