Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here she comes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ww... What!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell what you're looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghost has come
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghost of the girl that was killed in the park nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghost of the girl that was killed in the park nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her spirit has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it's a real ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She may already be in this apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phooey! Ghosts my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone must have crawled up the wall to the second floor and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,stuck his head out of the window to frighten us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK. but here is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:22.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:30.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one can crawl up to and stand here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,becuse there is no veranda or anything like that on this window
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it didn't look like a human figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The outline of it wiggled like jelly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the shadow already started losing shape
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before the window opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a demon burning to ashes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when the morning sun, touches it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've also seen her in the window before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was too painful to look at her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it stands to reason that she disappeared like ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because that ghost is supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the restless soul of Ms. Rui Tabuchi who
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was burned to death in the park four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ms. Rui Tabuchi'yg
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her drivers license narrowly escaped burning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her driver's license narrowly escaped burning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police said that her'teeth matched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long as the two guys who killed her don't get arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,her soul will never rest\NIn peace and go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-The two guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't there any witnesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A,person who happened to be passing by the park after midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saw two men nearby staring at the burning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as you-can also see on the poster that is
