Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a portrait of one of the two murderers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An evil looking guy with a scar-across his cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another guy was with him\NIn the park, but
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his face couldn't be seen because it was dark
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the old man that was here a while ago is the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who had been living here from before the incident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He-Hey! Did she appear again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Bugs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A moth is on your arm, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pg he\NMoths... are very common around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It probably came in through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear that lots of moths are\NIiving in the park where
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the incident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1 hey often fly over here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because this apartment is right in front of the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a moth! Out out the noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She completely screwed up this ghostly mood, for god's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think her screaming was just great
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop all this racket, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The strange shadow that we just saw
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was probably only a reflection of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,one of us on the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:16.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we stay here, nothing good will happen to us
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Conan.
